The,Wait,Time,Calculator,is,a,simple,API,that,allows,users,to,clock,wait,times,at,polling,locations,around,the,US,The,API,also,lets,users,report,this,data,and,display,it,on,a,Google,map,Developers,can,use,this,information,in,their,own,applications,and,websites,The,API,returns,poll,locations,by,address,or,latitude,and,longitude,optionally,returning,wait,times,national,wait,time,statistics,by,state,or,for,a,specific,poll,location,and,record,a,wait,time,for,a,specific,poll,location,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON